quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,49,"Fún àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi ní ìró pé dájúdájú Èmi ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  15,50,"Àti pé dájúdájú ìyà Mi ni ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro."
  15,51,"Fún wọn ní ìró nípa àlejò (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm."
  16,28,"(Àwọn ni) àwọn tí mọlāika ń pa nígbà tí wọ́n ń ṣàbòsí sí ẹ̀mí ara wọn lọ́wọ́. Ní àsìkò yìí ni wọ́n juwọ́ jusẹ̀ sílẹ̀ (wọ́n sì wí pé): “Àwa kò ṣe iṣẹ́ aburú kan kan.” Bẹ́ẹ̀ ni! Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Onímọ̀ nípa ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́."
  16,29,"Nítorí náà, ẹ wọ àwọn ẹnu ọ̀nà Iná lọ, olùṣegbére ni yín nínú rẹ̀. Ibùgbé àwọn onígbèéraga sì burú."
  16,30,"Wọ́n sọ fún àwọn tó bẹ̀rù (Allāhu) pé: “Kí ni Olúwa yín sọ̀kalẹ̀? Wọ́n á wí pé: “Rere ni.” Rere ti wà fún àwọn tó ṣe rere ní ilé ayé yìí. Dájúdájú Ilé Ìkẹ́yìn lóore jùlọ. Àti pé dájúdájú ilé àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu) dára."